      "title": "",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e小U最近锅多如狗，因为有一堆的人要找他调代码。一共有\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-1\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-2\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-1\"\u003en\u003c/script\u003e 个人要找他办事 。他们做了一道国家集训队的一道神题\u003cdel\u003e，要用到可持久化 Top cactus 等算法\u003c/del\u003e，但是他们都没有把代码调出来。他们分别编号为 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-3\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-4\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-5\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0.222em;\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-6\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-7\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0.222em;\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-8\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e…\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-9\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0.222em;\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-10\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-2\"\u003e1, 2, \\ldots, n\u003c/script\u003e，且编号从小到大排成一列。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小U想把他们按编号分成各批，然后\u003cstrong\u003e从前往后（即编号从小到大）\u003c/strong\u003e分批调代码。其中\u003cstrong\u003e每一批人的编号是连续的一段\u003c/strong\u003e。第 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-11\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-12\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-3\"\u003ei\u003c/script\u003e 个人调出代码需要 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-13\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-14\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-15\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003et\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-16\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-4\"\u003et_i\u003c/script\u003e 个单位时间。而每一批蒟蒻需要把代码都调好，才能出来。也就是说，他们占用教室的时间为\u003cstrong\u003e每个人调代码所需时间的最大值\u003c/strong\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e由于同学Gayfriends之间容易互相影响，每一批蒟蒻内编号最大的人，设编号为 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-17\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-18\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-5\"\u003ei\u003c/script\u003e，不能与编号为 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-19\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-20\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-21\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003el\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-22\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6\"\u003el_i\u003c/script\u003e 的人在同一批，否则这一批的代码会调不出来。如果 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-23\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-24\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-25\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003el\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-26\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-27\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-28\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-7\"\u003el_i = 0\u003c/script\u003e，就意味着没有这个限制这位同学是个纯洁的好孩子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而每位蒟蒻都会有不耐烦指数。第 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-29\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-30\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-8\"\u003ei\u003c/script\u003e 位蒟蒻每等待一个单位时间，他的不耐烦程度就会增加 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-31\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-32\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-33\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003ew\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-34\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-9\"\u003ew_i\u003c/script\u003e。等待时间指的是从他们排好队到这个蒟蒻进教室为止的这段时间，也就是排在他前面的每一批蒟蒻占用教室时间之和。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在小U想让他们成功调出这道神题，并且不耐烦程度的和最小。可是他忙着帮助他们，就把这个任务交给了你。\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "输入格式",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e第一行一个正整数 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-35\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-36\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-10\"\u003en\u003c/script\u003e，表示人数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e接下来 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-37\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-38\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-11\"\u003en\u003c/script\u003e 行每行三个非负整数 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\"\u003el_i, t_i, w_i​\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\"\u003el_i, t_i, w_i​\u003c/script\u003e，意义如题面所述。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保证 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\"\u003e0 \\leq l_i \\lt i\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\"\u003e0 \\leq l_i \\lt i\u003c/script\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "输出格式",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e仅一行，表示\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\"\u003en\u003c/script\u003e个人的最小不耐烦程度之和。\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "限制与约定",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e本题有 5 个子任务。对于所有数据，有 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\"\u003e0 \\leq t_i, w_i \\leq 10^9\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\"\u003e0 \\leq t_i, w_i \\leq 10^9\u003c/script\u003e，且最终答案不大于 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\"\u003e10^{18}\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\"\u003e10^{18}\u003c/script\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSubtask 1 (9 pts): \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-81\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-82\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-83\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-84\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-85\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-86\"\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-17\"\u003e1 \\leq n \\leq 10\u003c/script\u003e；  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSubtask 2 (10 pts): \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-87\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-88\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-89\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-90\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-91\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-92\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mspace\" id=\"MJXp-Span-93\" style=\"width: 0.167em; height: 0em;\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-94\"\u003e000\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-18\"\u003e1 \\leq n \\leq 2\\,000\u003c/script\u003e；  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSubtask 3 (18 pts): \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-95\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-96\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-97\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-98\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-99\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-100\"\u003e100\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mspace\" id=\"MJXp-Span-101\" style=\"width: 0.167em; height: 0em;\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-102\"\u003e000\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-19\"\u003e1 \\leq n \\leq 100\\,000\u003c/script\u003e 且 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-103\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-104\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-105\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003ew\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-106\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-20\"\u003ew_i\u003c/script\u003e，\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-107\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-108\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-109\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003et\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-110\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-21\"\u003et_i\u003c/script\u003e 均为一定范围内等概率随机生成；  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSubtask 4 (12 pts): \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-111\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-112\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-113\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-114\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-115\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-116\"\u003e100\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mspace\" id=\"MJXp-Span-117\" style=\"width: 0.167em; height: 0em;\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-118\"\u003e000\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-22\"\u003e1 \\leq n \\leq 100\\,000\u003c/script\u003e 且 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-119\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-120\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-121\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003et\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-122\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-123\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-124\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-125\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003et\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mrow MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-126\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-127\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-128\"\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-129\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-23\"\u003et_i \\leq t_{i+1}\u003c/script\u003e；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSubtask 5 (51 pts): \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-130\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-131\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-132\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-133\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-134\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-135\"\u003e100\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mspace\" id=\"MJXp-Span-136\" style=\"width: 0.167em; height: 0em;\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-137\"\u003e000\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-24\"\u003e1 \\leq n \\leq 100\\,000\u003c/script\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e",
